Class MainForm

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.application.Application
      • MainForm

  • public class MainForm
extends javafx.application.Application
    this is the main class for this application. It is responsible for all things that have to display to the user. this includes the tableviews, the create forms, and the login screen
